## Shared Folder

### `Game/Shared`
Used only when duplication is worse than coupling.

Allowed:
- base interfaces
- shared utilities
- cross-feature value objects
- cross-feature events

Rules:
- No feature-specific logic here.
- No Unity scene knowledge.

